                  <rs id="t18790210-218-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18790210-218-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18790210-218-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>, Feloniously entering a dwelling-house in the night, with intent to commit felony.</rs>
