                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">examined by the Prisoner</hi>). When you left my house you were drunk—that would be from 2.30 to 3, to the best of my knowledge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The Prisoner, in his defence, stated that he was drunk, and could not account for being in the shop.</hi>
